msgid "Options"
msgstr "Väljare"

#. Tag: option
#: man-kmymoney.1.docbook:136
#, no-c-format
msgid "--lang"
msgstr "--lang"

#. Tag: para
#: man-kmymoney.1.docbook:138
#, no-c-format
msgid "Language to be used"
msgstr "Språk att använda"

#. Tag: option
#: man-kmymoney.1.docbook:143
#, no-c-format
msgid "<option>-n</option>"
msgstr "<option>-n</option>"

#. Tag: para
#: man-kmymoney.1.docbook:145
#, no-c-format
msgid "Do not open last used file"
msgstr "Öppna inte senast använda fil"

#. Tag: option
#: man-kmymoney.1.docbook:150
#, no-c-format
msgid "--timers"
msgstr "--timers"

#. Tag: para
#: man-kmymoney.1.docbook:152
#, no-c-format
msgid "Enable performance timers"
msgstr "Aktivera prestandatidmätning"

#. Tag: option
#: man-kmymoney.1.docbook:157
#, no-c-format
msgid "--nocatch"
msgstr "--nocatch"

#. Tag: para
#: man-kmymoney.1.docbook:159
#, no-c-format
msgid "Do not globally catch uncaught exceptions"
msgstr "Fånga inte globalt ofångade undantag"

#. Tag: option
#: man-kmymoney.1.docbook:164
#, no-c-format
msgid "--trace"
msgstr "--trace"

#. Tag: para
#: man-kmymoney.1.docbook:166
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Turn on program traces. This option is only available when &kmymoney; is "
"compiled in debug mode."
msgstr ""
"Sätt på programspårning. Alternativet är bara tillgängligt när &kmymoney; "
"har kompilerats i avlusningsläge."

#. Tag: option
#: man-kmymoney.1.docbook:174
#, no-c-format
msgid "--dump-actions"
msgstr "--dump-actions"

#. Tag: para
#: man-kmymoney.1.docbook:176
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Dump the names of all defined QAction objects to stdout and quit. This "
"option is only available when &kmymoney; is compiled in debug mode."
msgstr ""
"Skriv ut namnen på alla definierade QAction-objekt på standardutmatningen "
"och avsluta. Alternativet är bara tillgängligt när &kmymoney; har "
"kompilerats i avlusningsläge."

#. Tag: title
#: man-kmymoney.1.docbook:189
#, no-c-format
msgid "See Also"
msgstr "Se också"

#. Tag: member
#: man-kmymoney.1.docbook:192
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The full documentation for &kmymoney; is maintained as a docbook manual. If "
"the &khelpcenter; program is properly installed at your site, the command "
"<userinput> <command>khelpcenter</command> <parameter>help:/kmymoney</"
"parameter> </userinput> should give you access to the complete manual. "
"Alternatively the manual can be browsed in &konqueror; giving it the "
"<acronym>URL</acronym> <ulink url=\"help:/kmymoney\">help:/kmymoney</ulink>"
msgstr ""
"Den fullständiga dokumentationen av &kmymoney; underhålls som en handbok i "
"Docbook. Om programmet &khelpcenter; är riktigt installerat på datorn, ska "
"kommandot <userinput><command>khelpcenter</command> <parameter>help:/"
"kmymoney</parameter></userinput> ge tillgång till den fullständiga "
"handboken. Som alternativ kan man bläddra i handboken med &konqueror;, genom "
"att ange webbadressen <ulink url=\"help:/kmymoney\">help:/kmymoney</ulink>."

